long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
WebRank SEO is one of the best Google Chrome SEO extension. WebRank SEO gives you Alexa Rank, traffic graphs, website security, server location, pages indexed and backlinks in various search engines(Google and Bing). A Search Engine Optimization(SEO) Tool for competitive analysis and website analysis. You can analyze your competitors just by one click. You can see domain whois information. Also you can check your website growth and compare your website with your competitors.

You can also try WebRank Toolbar for Firefox(https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/addon/52177) from the official website.
The same user experience and website analysis, now available on Android. Click here to go to Android Market(https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.probcomp.webrankstats)

For updates follow us on Twitter(http://twitter.com/webrankstats) or become a fan on Facebook(http://facebook.com/WebRankStats).

WebRank SEO FEATURES :-
"""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
- Alexa Rank
- Traffic Graphs
    * Alexa - Daily Traffic Rank
    * Alexa - Search Visit
- Pages indexed in Google
- Pages indexed in Bing
- Backlinks according to Google
- Whois Information
- "Compare Stats" button to Compare website with other websites.
- "Diff Stats" button to check progress of your website.
- Geo IP Location of the Website.
- Website Security check
    * Web of Trust (WOT)
    * McAfee SiteAdvisor
    * Norton Safeweb

And click on each to get more information about it.

You can also view website ranks, number of pages indexed, back links and other information online at  http://www.webrankstats.com.
By using this extension you must agree to privacy policy available at http://www.webrankstats.com/privacy-policy.html
